The mention of integrating theories into proof theory suggests that the paper may also belong to the category of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), as this is an area that deals with the organization and manipulation of data. Finally, the mention of research groups working on integrating theories into proof theory suggests that the paper may also belong to the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE), as this is an area that deals with the design and development of software systems.
